Carrefour Belgium Should Break Even in 2010, L’Echo Reports

-- B y   A n d r e w   C l a p h a m
-- 
2011-02-17T07:20:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-17/carrefour-belgium-should-break-even-in-2010-l-echo-reports.html
  Carrefour SA ’s Belgian unit should
break even in 2010, its executive director Gerard Lavinay said
in an interview with L’Echo.  “We should break even in 2010 and even make a small profit
in 2011,” Lavinay told the newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
